              Add Image relative to the lesson subject, this's not must but (recommended).
            </li>
            <li>
              Make Sure To Add Correct Lesson Number, recommended to look at the last lesson number for same unit before add this (lesson
              number).
            </li>
            <li>
              Carefully add lesson information to avoid conflicts.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div> -->
            </div>

        </div>

        <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>

</body>

</html>